## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible effects of anxiety on family and friends. The impact of anxiety can vary significantly depending on individual circumstances, the severity of the disorder, and the support systems in place. Additionally, some sources may not be up-to-date, and the information may not reflect the latest research developments in the field of mental health.